{"tid":509521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋兩住客爭執 50歲阿叔放火險燒死3鄰居","createTime":"2017-12-25T11:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T19:26:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4161ed33c12b798a3ce4f8a44500322de38c6678","tid":509521,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"青衣發生縱火事件，下午5時許，長發邨敬發樓兩住客因事爭執，事發其中一名年約50歲的男住客在對方門口淋液體放火，冒出大量濃煙，約20多名居民見狀到街上暫避。消防接報趕至，迅速將火救熄，救出屋內的2男1女，他們聲稱受傷，須由救護車送院治理。警方在後樓梯撿獲一把刀，懷疑與案有關，暫列縱火案，正追緝涉放火的男住客。"},{"pid":"ac40bc41b0431a725008c04ba1aefd94982c4a49","tid":509521,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9580f7f6fe5592b28a3960dcd96ff3e7cf1d49a6","tid":509521,"uid":23973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"估唔到我今日要去死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/509530/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/509530/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bbadf94f50b43acd5827e5e0f17cea331d08c0","tid":509521,"uid":7138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac40bc41b0431a725008c04ba1aefd94982c4a49","tid":509521,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"觸景傷情??"},{"pid":"e4f6bc242556ce436890c9632a3b65d5ee100ec1","tid":509521,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7555b988091b92f6968cf39a838f13a2c392a37","tid":509521,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾公屋狗 一鑊熟啦屌"},{"pid":"a00b9d681c1f45492b81d68f56895e95b7c8348f","tid":509521,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0